return ['messages'=>['/high-jewellery/'=>'https://eji.com.hk/zh-hans/%e9%ab%98%e7%ba%a7%e7%8f%a0%e5%ae%9d/','<p>A tribute of resilience and perseverance, the Lifeboat diamond pendant, crafted from the finest 18K yellow gold, reminds us of our brightest tomorrows amidst a sea of possibilities. It embarks on a journey of adventures and gives us a spirit of endurance for whatever challenges in life.</p>'=>'<p>这款救生艇钻石坠饰是对韧性和坚持的致敬。采用最优质的18K黄金制作，提醒我们在无限可能的海洋中坚持追求光明的明天。它象征着冒险的旅程，赋予我们面对各种挑战的坚韧精神。 </p>','<p>At the heart sits a striking sailboat glistening in silvery brilliance, every jewellery piece of the <em>Splendid Voyage</em> is artfully crafted to pursue and experience the beauty of life, ready to voyage and embark on a journey of imagination. Exploring our extraordinary selections, from the exquisite diamond arm rings to the minimalist geometric brooches and designer necklaces, each piece is designed to be disassembled and transformed into exquisite diamond jewellery.</p>'=>'<p>在心中坐落着一艘闪耀光辉的帆船 — <em>璀璨之航</em> 系列每一件珠宝作品都经精心打造，旨在追求与体验生活的美好，随时准备启航，展开一段想像之旅。<br>探索我们这非凡系列，从精美的钻石臂环，到极简几何胸针和设计项链，每件作品均可拆卸，并转化为精致的钻石珠宝。 </p>','<p>Crafted with 18K yellow gold and diamonds, these geometric sail brooches capture minimalist elegance with sharp and linear designs. Sleek and sophisticated, these brooches bring a subtle touch of glamorousness, navigating the sailboat on the open sea.</p>'=>'<p>以18K黄金和钻石精心制作的几何帆船胸针，以尖锐线条设计捕捉了极简主义的优雅，流畅而精致。这胸针为您的造型增添了一丝微妙的奢华感，犹如在开阔的海洋上驶向远方的帆船。 </p>','<p>Featuring an anchor motif – a signature nautical inspiration of strength, hope and stability, these anchors can be transformed into a pair of extraordinary earrings precisely crafted with gold and diamonds.</p>'=>'<p>这对耳环以锚为主题，象征力量、希望与稳定，黄金和钻石巧妙融合，展现独特的航海灵感。</p>','<p>Setting out into the vast ocean with nothing but the wind, the waves and the sails is a fun and thrilling adventure like no other. Fueling with passion for sailing, these exquisite diamond arm rings shimmering in two different patterns, intricate sophisticated craftsmanship and textures – allowing you to set sail in artistic styles.</p>'=>'<p>踏上广阔的海洋，唯有风、浪和帆——这是一场独特而激动人心的冒险。这些精美的钻石臂环以两种图案闪耀，展现出精致而复杂的工艺与质感，让您优雅启航。 </p>','<p>The sea, once it casts its spell, holds one in its net of wonder forever. The vastness and beauty of the sea have always been a source of inspiration. There’s nothing quite like sailing on the open sea. The best part of our Splendid Voyage is – the infinite imagination always reminds us that possibility awaits in life. From brilliant diamonds to the unique nautical-inspired designs, each piece of jewellery showcases exceptional artistry and ingenious style, yearning for adventure and determination to forge ahead.</p><p>Having been dazzled by our Splendid Voyage collection, we dream big dreams! At EJI, our imagination and creativity run wild. We remain dedicated to bringing our passion and pursuit in excellence and craftsmanship to life. We’re all ears and ready to help you create one-of-a-kind piece with our bespoke jewellery service – make your big dreams come true!</p>'=>'<p>海洋的广阔与美丽始终是灵感的源泉，没什么比海上航行更令人陶醉。壮丽航程最美好的部分在于——无尽想像力总是提醒着我们，生活充满了可能性。    </p><p>从璀璨钻石，到独特的航海灵感设计，每一件珠宝都展现了卓越的艺术性和巧妙风格，渴望冒险并坚定向前。在EJI，我们致力发挥想像力和创造力，将我们对卓越工艺的追求化为现实。我们随时倾听，助您创造独一无二的珠宝，让您梦想成真。   </p>','<p>This splendid nautical burgee pendant draws inspiration from the essence of maritime traditions. It is meticulously crafted with shimmering diamonds – bringing a touch of elegance to the sailboat and evoking the twinkling reflections dancing on the surface of the rough sea.</p>'=>'<p>这华丽的航海旗吊坠融合了海洋的精髓，以闪耀钻石制作，为帆船增添优雅，唤起在波涛汹涌的海面上跳动的闪烁倒影。 </p>','Anchor Earrings'=>'锚形耳环','GEOMETRIC SAIL BROOCHES​​'=>'几何帆船胸针','High Jewellery'=>'高级珠宝','Home'=>'首页','Jewel Treasure I'=>'珠宝珍宝 I','Jewel Treasure II'=>'珠宝珍宝 II','Jewel Treasure III'=>'珠宝珍宝 III','Jewel Treasure IV'=>'珠宝珍宝 IV','Jewel Treasure V'=>'珠宝珍宝 V','Lifeboat Pendant'=>'救生艇吊坠','Nautical Burgee Pendant'=>'航海旗吊坠','Sail Arm Rings'=>'帆船臂环','Set sail and embark on your adventu